<h2 id="hvac-specific-features">HVAC-Specific Features and Value</h2>

<div class="prose max-w-none">
<p>Workiz includes several features that matter specifically to HVAC contractors:</p>

<p><strong>Equipment Tracking:</strong> Track warranty information, service history, and replacement schedules for HVAC units. Available on Professional and Premium plans. This feature alone saves HVAC companies $200-500 monthly in administrative time.</p>

<p><strong>Recurring Service Agreements:</strong> Automate billing for maintenance contracts. Professional plan and above. HVAC companies using this feature report 23% higher customer retention and $50K-150K additional annual recurring revenue.</p>

<p><strong>Photo Documentation:</strong> Before/after photos with automatic job attachment. All plans include unlimited photo storage. Essential for warranty claims and customer communication.</p>

<p><strong>HVAC-Specific Templates:</strong> Pre-built estimates for common services like tune-ups, installations, and repairs. Premium plan includes custom template builder.</p>

<p>However, Workiz lacks some advanced HVAC features found in <a href="/hvac/pricing/servicetitan-pricing">ServiceTitan</a>, such as load calculations, equipment sizing tools, and advanced inventory management for large parts inventories.</p>
</div>

