<h2 id="hidden-costs">Hidden Costs and Add-Ons</h2>

<div class="prose max-w-none">
<p>Workiz's advertised pricing doesn't include several costs that HVAC companies encounter:</p>

<p><strong>Payment Processing Fees:</strong> 2.9% + $0.30 per credit card transaction, 1% (max $5) for ACH. A company processing $10,000 monthly pays $290 in card fees alone.</p>

<p><strong>SMS Messaging:</strong> $0.10 per SMS after 100 free messages monthly. HVAC companies average 300-500 SMS per month for appointment confirmations and updates, costing $20-40 extra.</p>

<p><strong>Advanced Reporting:</strong> Custom dashboards and advanced analytics require Premium plan ($199/month minimum). Basic reporting on lower plans lacks key HVAC metrics like technician utilization and parts profitability.</p>

<p><strong>API Access:</strong> Third-party integrations require Premium plan. Essential for connecting HVAC-specific tools like load calculation software or parts suppliers.</p>

<p><strong>Phone Support:</strong> Basic plan gets email support only. Phone support requires Professional plan ($99/month minimum). For HVAC emergencies, waiting hours for email responses isn't practical.</p>

<p><strong>Data Migration:</strong> Free for simple transfers, but complex migrations from systems like ServiceTitan cost $500-2,000 for professional migration services.</p>

<p>Total hidden costs typically add $100-200 monthly to your Workiz bill, depending on transaction volume and feature usage.</p>
</div>

